{"title_page": "Christian Brunner", "text_new": "{{short description|Swiss cyclist}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox cyclist\n| name          = Christian Brunner\n| image         = \n| caption       = \n| fullname      = \n| nickname      = \n| birth_date    = {{birth date and age|1953|4|2|df=yes}}\n| birth_place   = \n| death_date    = \n| death_place   = \n| height        = \n| weight        = \n| currentteam   = \n| discipline    = \n| role          = \n| ridertype     = \n| amateuryears1 = \n| amateurteam1  = \n| proyears1     = \n| proteam1      = \n| majorwins     = \n}}\n\n'''Christian Brunner''' (born 2 April 1953) is a former Swiss [[cycling|cyclist]]. He competed in the [[Cycling at the 1972 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 1000m time trial|1000m time trial]] and [[Cycling at the 1972 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's team pursuit|team pursuit]] events at the [[1972 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"sports-reference\">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/br/christian-brunner-1.html |title=Christian Brunner Olympic Results |accessdate=31 October 2014 |work=sports-reference.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Brunner, Christian}}\n[[Category:1953 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Swiss male cyclists]]\n[[Category:Olympic cyclists of Switzerland]]\n[[Category:Cyclists at the 1972 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n\n\n{{Switzerland-cycling-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Swiss cyclist}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2014}}\n{{Infobox cyclist\n| name          = Christian Brunner\n| image         = \n| caption       = \n| fullname      = \n| nickname      = \n| birth_date    = {{birth date and age|1953|4|2|df=yes}}\n| birth_place   = \n| death_date    = \n| death_place   = \n| height        = \n| weight        = \n| currentteam   = \n| discipline    = \n| role          = \n| ridertype     = \n| amateuryears1 = \n| a